dialog.body: Welcome to Old Stone Auto Insurance! My name is Matthew King. May I have your name, please?
Hello, my name is Natalie Phillips.
Nice to meet you, Natalie. Can you please provide me with your policy number?
Sure, it's four five six two three.
Thank you, Natalie. Could you also confirm your date of birth for verification purposes?
Of course, it's the twentieth of July, nineteen seventy-eight.
Thank you for confirming, Natalie. How can I assist you today with your policy or any other inquiries?
I would like to add a new vehicle to my policy.
I can help you with that. Let's gather the details of the vehicle. Thank you for your time, Natalie. Is there anything else you would like to discuss today?
No, that's all for now. Thank you for your assistance, Matthew.
You're welcome, Natalie. Have a great day!
